                </RzParagraph>

                <RzAlert Variant="AlertVariant.Information" class="my-5">
                    <AlertTitle>üí° Tip: Tailwind for JavaScript</AlertTitle>
                    <AlertDescription>
                        Alpine is often described as ‚Äúthe Tailwind CSS of JavaScript.‚Äù If you‚Äôre comfortable adding utility classes to your markup, you‚Äôll feel right at home adding Alpine directives like <code>x-data</code> and <code>x-on:click</code>.
                    </AlertDescription>
