            </section>

            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="A First Glimpse">
                    A First Glimpse
                </RzHeading>
                <RzParagraph>
                    Here‚Äôs a simple example to show you what Alpine.js looks like in action. It‚Äôs a button that toggles a message on and off, right in the browser.
                </RzParagraph>
                
                <RzBrowser Layout="typeof(PreviewLayout)">
