                        However, if you use <code>rizzyui-csp.js</code> for enhanced security, Alpine.js cannot execute inline JavaScript expressions like <code>open = !open</code>. In that case, you must move logic into methods within a co-located JavaScript file. We'll cover this recommended "code-behind" pattern in the next sections.
                    </AlertDescription>
                </RzAlert>
